        <t:abstract>
           <t:p>
              A theological treatise believed to be a response of king <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4428Galawdew">Galāwdewos</t:persName> 
              to the Jesuit missionaries headed by <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7691Oviedo">Oviedo</t:persName>.
           </t:p>
        </t:abstract>
